NEWSFLASH!<br>
Verant has never liked FD pulling and only tolerates it because so many monks whine that that's their sole reason for being.<br>
<br>
NEWSFLASH!<br>
FD pulling is an art and if you're getting hit so much now that AC will matter that much, you're not an artist.  FD pulling melee mobs where AC matters is a joke compared to pulling caster mobs where it doesn't matter.  A few points of AC won't save you when FD fails.<br>
<br>
NEWSFLASH!<br>
Monks we're always suposed to do max toe-to-toe damage.  That is their sole purpose in life.  FD pulling is a &quot;perk&quot; for those who like doing it and is, IMHO, way overused vs other pulling methods.<br>
